{"tid":2478124,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紐約襲擊亞裔疑犯多患精神病 疫情下缺支援易發作","createTime":"2021-04-06T21:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-06T22:10:07.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"67f96c64b9126a489b0fa88f42c236f5b7c1af9b","tid":2478124,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T21:26:37.000Z","msg":"（北美通訊）美國紐約市警察局（NYPD）表示，上月下旬針對亞裔仇恨襲擊的7名被捕人士當中，五人患有精神病，需要接受治療；餘下兩人也有精神病徵狀。警方表示，這些疑犯過去沒有得到適當治療，經常進出監獄，且有濫藥問題。紐約市警察局局長謝伊（Dermot Shea）上周五表示，除了種族仇恨問題，當局亦需正視相關精神健康問題。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210407/B5W5TE6Z7RCAVF4N3RK74VG2WY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210407%2FB5W5TE6Z7RCAVF4N3RK74VG2WY%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=d026fc41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210407%2FB5W5TE6Z7RCAVF4N3RK74VG2WY%2F&h=052f3296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210407/B5W5TE6Z7RCAVF4N3RK74VG2WY/</a>"},{"pid":"f06a05d0e8217ceb5258ad67c3710100b4dc7726","tid":2478124,"uid":3063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T21:33:54.000Z","msg":"精神病LM"},{"pid":"7497178c34dc5b83939e088bcedd7b995a1a68da","tid":2478124,"uid":251696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T22:10:07.000Z","msg":"感覺美國佬用同一招玩野"}]}